
================================================================

What is Alix
--------------------------------

Alix is a family of reliable, robust, superior quality communications computers

 http://pcengines.ch/alix.htm

================================================================

How to Boot the Alix
--------------------------------

1. Connect the DB-9 serial port on the Alix to your system.  This 
   will allow you to view the console output.  Console is 115200 bps.

2. Insert the CF card into your Alix

3. Power on the Alix by plugging it in


